text: George Wilde or George Wylde may refer to: * George Wylde I (or Wilde; 1550–1616), English lawyer and politician * George Wylde II (or Wilde; 1594–1650), English lawyer and politician (son of the above) * George Wilde (bishop) (1610–1665), bishop of Derry * George Wilde (American football) (1923–1975), American football player ==See also== * George Wild (footballer) * George Wyld (1821-1906), Scottish homeopathic physician and Christian Theosophist
title: George Wilde
